[
    {
        "text": "Hello! Welcome to \"Michael's Better Business English\".",
        "startTime": 560,
        "endTime": 3786,
        "slowStartTime": 990,
        "slowEndTime": 5904
    },
    {
        "text": "This month we're looking at how to be tactful.",
        "startTime": 4409,
        "endTime": 7074,
        "slowStartTime": 6764,
        "slowEndTime": 10836
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, tactful is a little bit of a difficult word.",
        "startTime": 8029,
        "endTime": 10110,
        "slowStartTime": 12193,
        "slowEndTime": 15390
    },
    {
        "text": "Tactful means to be sensitive, to avoid hurting other people's feelings.",
        "startTime": 10817,
        "endTime": 16365,
        "slowStartTime": 16376,
        "slowEndTime": 24772
    },
    {
        "text": "This is very important when you're giving bad news,...",
        "startTime": 17071,
        "endTime": 20433,
        "slowStartTime": 25757,
        "slowEndTime": 30875
    },
    {
        "text": "...introducing a negative topic, or criticizing someone.",
        "startTime": 20845,
        "endTime": 24215,
        "slowStartTime": 31418,
        "slowEndTime": 36548
    },
    {
        "text": "How can you do this?",
        "startTime": 25398,
        "endTime": 26523,
        "slowStartTime": 38247,
        "slowEndTime": 40009
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, there are three steps to being tactful.",
        "startTime": 27091,
        "endTime": 29729,
        "slowStartTime": 40787,
        "slowEndTime": 44819
    },
    {
        "text": "Step one, signal.",
        "startTime": 30619,
        "endTime": 32321,
        "slowStartTime": 46078,
        "slowEndTime": 48706
    },
    {
        "text": "Signal means to signal to the listener some bad news or negative topic is coming.",
        "startTime": 33076,
        "endTime": 38431,
        "slowStartTime": 49764,
        "slowEndTime": 57872
    },
    {
        "text": "And we use words like, \"unfortunately,\" \"regrettably,\" \"with regret\".",
        "startTime": 39187,
        "endTime": 44824,
        "slowStartTime": 58930,
        "slowEndTime": 67461
    },
    {
        "text": "This lets the listener know something bad is coming and it helps them prepare.",
        "startTime": 45869,
        "endTime": 50430,
        "slowStartTime": 68953,
        "slowEndTime": 75870
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, use some kind of qualifier.",
        "startTime": 51769,
        "endTime": 54572,
        "slowStartTime": 77803,
        "slowEndTime": 82083
    },
    {
        "text": "A qualifier is some expression like \"it seems\" or \"it appears\".",
        "startTime": 55605,
        "endTime": 60952,
        "slowStartTime": 83557,
        "slowEndTime": 91653
    },
    {
        "text": "This has a softening effect.",
        "startTime": 61435,
        "endTime": 63400,
        "slowStartTime": 92303,
        "slowEndTime": 95325
    },
    {
        "text": "Third, use a modifier.",
        "startTime": 65103,
        "endTime": 67186,
        "slowStartTime": 97804,
        "slowEndTime": 101004
    },
    {
        "text": "Modifiers are words like \"slight\" or \"small\".",
        "startTime": 68038,
        "endTime": 71370,
        "slowStartTime": 102207,
        "slowEndTime": 107280
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"We have a slight problem with the delivery.\"",
        "startTime": 71931,
        "endTime": 74883,
        "slowStartTime": 108047,
        "slowEndTime": 112550
    },
    {
        "text": "These words make it feel less and underplay the negative topic.",
        "startTime": 75867,
        "endTime": 81169,
        "slowStartTime": 113950,
        "slowEndTime": 121979
    },
    {
        "text": "So, being tactful is not easy.",
        "startTime": 82381,
        "endTime": 84509,
        "slowStartTime": 123722,
        "slowEndTime": 126989
    },
    {
        "text": "But by using these three steps, you can do it.",
        "startTime": 84906,
        "endTime": 87929,
        "slowStartTime": 127509,
        "slowEndTime": 132119
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck.",
        "startTime": 88773,
        "endTime": 89949,
        "slowStartTime": 133310,
        "slowEndTime": 135148
    }
]